title: Raw Cattle Hide Stocks in Hands of Tanners for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1918-1933 (2)--Original Data, 1934-1945. Source: Data For December 1918-May 1920: Report Of The Federal Trade Commission On Shoe And Leather Costs And Prices, June 10, 1921, Table 3, P. 150; Data For June-November 1920: Merchants' National Bank Of Boston, Monthly Statistical Summary On The Hide And Leather Industry, 1921 And 1922; Data For December 1920-1921: U.S. Bureau Of The Census, Report On Hides, Skins, And Leather; Data For 1922-1933: Tanners' Council Of America, Direct From Files
